{"type":"text","timestamp":1783488358962,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd247cdffejTvcrmloecAup3","part":{"id":"prt_f403071dd001HAwegTOH0NULMY","messageID":"msg_f402f85c9001VkrW07kTPJyEM7","sessionID":"ses_0bfd247cdffejTvcrmloecAup3","type":"text","text":"Strong evidence gathered. Key independent finding already forming: the runtime→workflows coupling is via **absolute repo-root string paths** (in `compile-command-contracts.cjs`/`check-contract-drift.cjs`), NOT relative `require()` hops — only `artifact-root.cjs` (runtime→system-spec-kit) uses a real relative path that needs depth repair. This revises the plan's \"hop-count everywhere\" framing. Let me write phase_init outputs now.","time":{"start":1783488344541,"end":1783488358948}}}
