nds=452, advisor=264, agents=18×2, plugins=3, ci=1, prose=28.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"F3.2\", \"text\": \"Advisor already has merge-identity layer (aliases.ts:92-109); system-deep-loop is SECOND fold = id-rename of MERGED_DEEP_SKILL_ID.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"F3.3\", \"text\": \"Divergence-ledger reason strings are historical narration; mechanical replace corrupts them (REQ-007 ratchet guard).\"},\n    {\"id\": \"F3.5\", \"text\": \"skill-graph.json generated; hand-edit trap; edit graph-metadata.json sources + re-scan.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"F3.6\", \"text\": \"orchestrate.md hardcodes mode-registry.json path 3× ×2 agent trees = 6 critical edits.\"}\n  ],\n  \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n    {\"id\": \"R1.1\", \"text\": \"Single mechanical find/replace.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"R1.2\", \"text\": \"Reverse as larger per-site risk.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"R2.1\", \"text\": \"Mechanism A forward-only.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"R2.2\", \"text\": \"4 system-spec-kit edits suffice.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"R3.1\", \"text\": \"Advisor needs from-scratch merge layer.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"R3.2\", \"text\": \"Hand-edit skill-graph.json.\"},\n    {\"id\": \"R3.3\", \"text\": \"Mechanical full-file replace on divergence ledger.\"}\n  ]\n}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-3/deep-research-findings-registry.json"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-3/deep-research-findings-registry.json","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-3/deep-research-findings-registry.json","time":{"start":1783488938797,"end":1783488938800}},"id":"prt_f4039832b0010wlyolZF